econstruction in Jiankou, China on Tuesday.</media:description></media:content><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260512-great-wall-mb-1534-f5799e.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="3125" width="2500"><media:credit>Ignacio Torres</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Restoration along the Jiankou section of the Great Wall on Tuesday.</media:text><media:description type="plain">Construction workers at Phase 5 of the Great Wall reconstruction in Jiankou, China on Tuesday.</media:description></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/2560512-great-wall-mb-1651-298659.jpg" height="2500" width="2500"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Wed, 13 May 2026 01:04:28 GMT</pubDate><title>The Great Wall is being restored one brick at a time</title><updateDate>Wed, 13 May 2026 02:05:44 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dc:creator>Tom Llamas</dc:creator><dc:creator>Jennifer Jett</dc:creator><dc:creator>Jay Ganglani</dc:creator><dc:contributor>Dawn Liu</dc:contributor><dc:contributor>Erin Tan</dc:contributor><dateTimeWritten>Wed, 13 May 2026 01:08:37 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>China loves electric cars: making them, driving them and selling them to the rest of the world.</description><expires>2112-01-01T00:00:00.000+0000</expires><guid>https://www.nbcnews.com/world/asia/chinese-evs-take-world-storm-united-states-rcna344680</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/world/asia/chinese-evs-take-world-storm-united-states-rcna344680</link><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260512-byd-mb-1733-48a5e1.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1667" width="2500"><media:credit>Ignacio Torres</media:credit><media:text type="plain">BYC electric vehicles at a showroom in Beijing this week.</media:text><media:description type="plain">BYC electric vehicles at a showroom in Beijing this week.</media:description></media:content><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260513-byd-sealion-china-mn-0920-c0ac23.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1667" width="2500"><media:credit>Anna Ratkoglo</media:credit><media:text type="plain">China Auto Show</media:text><media:description type="plain">A BYD Sealion 05 is displayed during the 2026 Beijing International Automotive Exhibition at the New China International Exhibition Center (NCIEC) in Beijing, China. </media:description></media:content><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260512-tom-llamas-byd-mb-1718-e4771a.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1667" width="2500"><media:credit>Ignacio Torres</media:credit><media:text type="plain">NBC News&#39; Tom Llamas at a BYD dealership in Beijing this week.</media:text><media:description type="plain">NBC News&#39; Tom Llamas at a BYD dealership in Beijing this week.</media:description></media:content><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260507-byd-auto-mb-1728-1f6f3d.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1667" width="2500"><media:credit>Qilai Shen</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Beijing Auto Show 2026</media:text><media:description type="plain">A display of the BYD Denza e3 at the Beijing auto show on April 25. China&#39;s premier automotive event showcased the new technologies emerging out of cutthroat competition. </media:description></media:content><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260512-byd-mb-1741-aa192f.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1667" width="2500"><media:credit>AFP via Getty Images</media:credit><media:text type="plain">BYD&#39;s Shenzhen car carrier docked in the port of Suzhou, China on April 17.</media:text><media:description type="plain">BYD&#39;s Shenzhen car carrier docked in the port of Suzhou, China, on April 17.</media:description></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260512-byd-mb-1733-48a5e1.jpg" height="1667" width="2500"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Wed, 13 May 2026 01:08:37 GMT</pubDate><title>Chinese EVs take the world by storm — except in the U.S.</title><updateDate>Wed, 13 May 2026 01:18:56 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dateTimeWritten>Wed, 13 May 2026 13:09:22 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>How will Trump&#39;s China trip differ from his 2017 visit?</description><expires>2056-05-13T13:07:54.000+0000</expires><guid isPermaLink="false">f_vert_brk_tdy_llamas_beijing_260513</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/video/shorts/how-will-trump-s-china-trip-differ-from-his-2017-visit-263226437822</link><media:content url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/f_vert_brk_tdy_llamas_beijing_260513/1/abs/index.m3u8" medium="video"><media:credit></media:credit><media:title>How will Trump&#39;s China trip differ from his 2017 visit?</media:title><media:player url="https://www.nbcnews.com/video/shorts/how-will-trump-s-china-trip-differ-from-his-2017-visit-263226437822"></media:player><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/mpx/2704722219/2026_05/trump_xi-o4vqnr.jpg"></media:thumbnail><media:description type="plain">How will Trump&#39;s China trip differ from his 2017 visit?</media:description></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/mpx/2704722219/2026_05/trump_xi-o4vqnr.jpg"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Wed, 13 May 2026 12:02:56 GMT</pubDate><title>How will Trump&#39;s China trip differ from his 2017 visit?</title><updateDate>Wed, 13 May 2026 13:09:22 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dateTimeWritten>Wed, 13 May 2026 13:09:01 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>Air Force One landed at Beijing Capital International Airport in China. Trump’s state visit includes a b