/2026_05/1778684977251_now_brk_murdaugh_overturn_260513_S3_1920x1080-5ver1o.jpg"></media:thumbnail><media:description type="plain">The South Carolina Supreme Court has overturned Alex Murdaugh&#39;s double murder conviction and ordered a new trial in the killings of his wife and son. NBC News&#39; Laura Jarrett reports on the court&#39;s decision and what comes next for Murdaugh.</media:description><media:subTitle type="text/srt" lang="en-US" url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/nbcnews/captions/2026/05/1778684977251_now_brk_murdaugh_overturn_260513.srt"></media:subTitle><media:subTitle type="text/vtt" lang="en-US" url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/nbcnews/captions/2026/05/1778684977251_now_brk_murdaugh_overturn_260513.vtt"></media:subTitle></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/mpx/2704722219/2026_05/1778684977251_now_brk_murdaugh_overturn_260513_S3_1920x1080-5ver1o.jpg"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Wed, 13 May 2026 15:09:47 GMT</pubDate><title>Court overturns Alex Murdaugh&#39;s murder convictions and orders new trial</title><updateDate>Wed, 13 May 2026 15:10:56 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dc:creator>Adam Edelman</dc:creator><dc:contributor>Katie Taylor</dc:contributor><dateTimeWritten>Wed, 13 May 2026 18:50:49 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>After a series of court rulings gave Republicans a decisive advantage in the national redistricting fight, Democrats’ options for a counterpunch before this year’s midterms are limited.</description><expires>2112-01-01T00:00:00.000+0000</expires><guid>https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/2026-election/democrats-turn-state-legislative-races-catch-redistricting-battle-rcna344719</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/2026-election/democrats-turn-state-legislative-races-catch-redistricting-battle-rcna344719</link><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260513-redistricting-rs-7c1949.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1667" width="2500"><media:credit>Madison Thorn</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Trump Says Tennessee To Redraw District Maps To Boost GOP</media:text><media:description type="plain">Democrats are looking ahead to the next election cycle to respond to new Republican-drawn congressional maps in states like Tennessee.</media:description></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260513-redistricting-rs-7c1949.jpg" height="1667" width="2500"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Wed, 13 May 2026 18:50:49 GMT</pubDate><title>Democrats turn to state legislative races to catch up in the redistricting battle</title><updateDate>Wed, 13 May 2026 18:50:49 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dc:creator>Minyvonne Burke</dc:creator><dc:contributor>Shelley Osterloh</dc:contributor><dc:contributor>Doha Madani</dc:contributor><dateTimeWritten>Wed, 13 May 2026 15:00:19 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>The Utah grief author convicted of murder after prosecutors said she laced her husband’s cocktail with a fatal dose of fentanyl was sentenced to life in prison without parole on what would have been his 44th birthday.</description><expires>2112-01-01T00:00:00.000+0000</expires><guid>https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/utah-grief-author-convicted-husbands-poisoning-death-sentenced-rcna344887</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/utah-grief-author-convicted-husbands-poisoning-death-sentenced-rcna344887</link><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-03/2360316-kouri-richins-mn-1130-9ef0a7.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1666" width="2500"><media:credit>Spenser Heaps</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Kouri Richins Murder Trial</media:text><media:description type="plain">Kouri Richins during her murder trial at the Summit County Courthouse in Park City, Utah, on Feb. 23, 2026. 